{
  "texts": [
    "The implementation of the model is conducted on a 64-bit Windows Server 2019 computer featuring 2 GHz processor with Intel Xeon CPU, 384 GB RAM and eight cores.",
    "The CNN model is created with MAT-LAB R2018b.",
    "The model is 71.1% accurate for HC versus MCI and 88.9% accurate for HC versus AD respectively.",
    "There should be no overlap in the subject IDs between testing and training set.",
    "In the same directions, Mehmood et al. 2020 devised siamese CNN model for classifying dementia stages by drawing inspiration from the VGG16 architecture."
  ]
}